{"name":"Custom Inputs","tagline":"Custom radio buttons and checkboxes with jQuery","body":"# custom-inputs\r\n\r\n\r\nCustom radio buttons and checkboxes with jQuery\r\n\r\n## Markup\r\n\r\n### Checkboxes\r\n\r\n``` html\r\n  <ul class=\"custom-inputs\">\r\n    <li>\r\n      <input id=\"checkbox1\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"checkbox1\" value=\"1\">\r\n      <label for=\"checkbox2\">Checkbox 1</label>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <input id=\"checkbox2\" type=\"checkbox\" name=\"checkbox2\" value=\"2\">\r\n      <label for=\"checkbox2\">Checkbox 2</label>\r\n    </li>    \r\n  </ul>\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Radio Buttons\r\n\r\n``` html\r\n  <ul class=\"custom-inputs\">\r\n    <li>\r\n      <input id=\"radio1\" type=\"radio\" name=\"radio\" value=\"1\">\r\n      <label for=\"radio1\">Radio 1</label>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li>\r\n      <input id=\"radio2\" type=\"radio\" name=\"radio\" value=\"2\">\r\n      <label for=\"radio2\">Radio 2</label>\r\n    </li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Initialize\r\n\r\n### Checkboxes\r\n\r\n``` js\r\n  <script>\r\n    $('.custom-inputs').customInput('checkbox');\r\n  </script>\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Radio Buttons\r\n\r\n``` js\r\n  <script>\r\n    $('.custom-inputs').customInput('radio');\r\n  </script>\r\n```","google":"","note":"Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration."}